headline: Baxter to Host Annual Meeting of Stockholders in Virtual Format
summary: DEERFIELD, Ill., March 26, 2025--Baxter International Inc. (NYSE:BAX), a global medtech leader, will host its Annual Meeting of Stockholders (the 2025 Annual Meeting) in a virtual format on Tuesday, May 6, 2025 at 9 a.m., Central Time, as disclosed in Baxter’s proxy statement for the 2025 Annual Meeting.
